messages.ssml: <speak>According to the World Health Organization, the incubation period, the time between catching the novel coronavirus and showing symptoms of  the <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>  disease range from 1-14 days, most commonly around 5 days.</speak>

speech: According to the World Health Organization, the incubation period, the time between catching the novel coronavirus and showing symptoms of  the COVID-19 disease range from 1-14 days, most commonly around 5 days.
